{"TopicId":122021,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Changing Viewpoint while flying","CreatedByName":"Jaeleth","CreatedById":136435,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T08:28:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jaeleth","CreatedById":136435,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T08:28:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDo you know if there is a way to change focus to any part of a ship inflight (translation of the viewpoint) ? Like the shift key on the VAB.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Efor big ships it is hard to manage inflight parts that are far away from the CoM.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-10-01T21:56:42Z\u0022 title=\u002210/01/2015 09:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 1, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Jaeleth\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Feradose","CreatedById":111211,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T09:33:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlt\u0026amp;Right click dragging will move the camera... Quite awkwardly but it does the job.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T09:35:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMiddle click also drags the camera. I find that easier and more intuitive than alt-rightclick.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eddiew","CreatedById":127483,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T09:44:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Feradose\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Feradose\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAlt\u0026amp;Right click dragging will move the camera... Quite awkwardly but it does the job.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T10:10:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI know there\u0027s a way to reset the camera but never remember it. Hitting M twice (to go in and out of map mode) resets it though.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mystique","CreatedById":95628,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-09-30T10:13:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022eddiew\u0022 data-cite=\u0022eddiew\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E...I don\u0027t have a middle click, only a scroll wheel :S\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EErr.. Have you ever tried pressing that scroll wheel?)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Feradose","CreatedById":111211,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-01T08:52:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mystique\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mystique\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EErr.. Have you ever tried pressing that scroll wheel?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESometimes, they dont have sensors to detect clicking \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESource: a sad 2 months in life\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaeleth","CreatedById":136435,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-01T21:55:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks. It worked \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E but with some limitations:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eonly works when pressing Alt at the same time I press center mouse wheel\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}